1. *Dobro* je da se ova situacija promeni. (It is good that this situation changes.)

2. Ona je *dobra* prijateljica. (She is a good friend.)

3. Imamo *dobro* vreme. (We have good weather.)

4. Ja sam *dobar* učenik. (I am a good student.)

5. Oni su *dobri* ljudi. (They are good people.)

6. Ono je *dobro*. (That is good.)

7. *Dobro* je da se uči strani jezik. (It is good to learn a foreign language.)